<p class="MsoBodyText" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Book Antiqua&quot;;">Researchers and
practitioners are invited to submit <i style="">on or
before <b style="">February 28, 2009</b></i>, a 2-3
page chapter proposal clearly explaining the mission and concerns of
his or her
proposed chapter. Authors of accepted proposals will be notified by <b
 style=""><i style="">March
31, 2009 </i></b>about the status of their proposals and sent chapter
guidelines. Full chapters are expected to be submitted by <b style=""><i
 style="">June 20, 2009</i></b>. All
submitted chapters will be reviewed on a double-blind review basis. </span><span
 style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Book Antiqua&quot;;">This book is
scheduled to be published by IGI Global</span><span
